opkg instsall quagga quagga-bgpd quagga-libzebra quagga-zebra

### commands

/etc/init.d/quagga restart

### debugging

from cilium-agent:

tcpdump -n -i any tcp port 179

from openwrt:

nc localhost 2605

> show ip bgp summary
> show ip bgp
> show ip bgp neighbors

nc localhost 2601

> show ip route